        "heading_size": 160,
        "content": "<p>The IH-684 marks a first for Iron Heart Germany. Developed in close collaboration with Haraki-San and the Iron Heart Japan team, the 684 is the first cut initiated by Iron Heart Germany to become part of the global Iron Heart lineup.<br/>While the 684 will be integrated internationally in the future, the 16oz selvedge edition presented here remains exclusive to Iron Heart Germany.<br/>This project reflects partnership, trust and shared vision within the Iron Heart family.<br/>No experiment. A permanent addition.</p>",
