    "section_image_with_text_xLFbgw": {
      "type": "section-image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "section_height": "five-fifty-height",
        "layout": "inline",
        "image_location": "right",
        "image_width": "standard",
        "media_type": "image",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/684_Seite_ea0f3ee2-7fd7-41df-8fb2-7ee2b1068fbd.jpg",
        "video_file": "",
        "subheading": "The 684 Cut",
        "title": "<p>Relaxed Straight. Rooted in 634</p>",
        "heading_highlight_type": "circle",
        "highlight_color": "#d43747",
        "highlight_text_color": "#000000",
        "heading_size": 130,
        "content": "<p>The 684 is the widest fit Iron Heart has ever produced. It is based on the iconic 634, but with deliberate room through the leg.<br/><br/>It is a true relaxed straight fit: classic rise, room through the thigh, straight leg opening, no taper, and signature tobacco-coloured stitching throughout.<br/><br/>The goal was not to follow trends, but to create a wider proportion that feels natural within the Iron Heart philosophy. Not baggy. Not exaggerated. Not fashion-driven.<br/><br/>Clean lines, a stable stance, and a natural drape define the silhouette. A modern proportion that moves with the body instead of restricting it.<br/><br/>Wider. With intention. The 684 is here to stay.</p>",
        "text_alignment": "center",
        "button_text": "",
        "button_link": "",
        "button_color": "btn--black",
        "button_style": "btn--solid",
        "button_size": "btn--small",
