        "title": "<p>COMPLETING THE 684</p>",
        "heading_highlight_type": "circle",
        "highlight_color": "#d43747",
        "highlight_text_color": "#000000",
        "description": "<p>Every 684 comes in a 684-Tote Bag.</p><p>The 684 is more than a single garment. To complete the collection, we developed two pieces built with the same mindset: durability, texture, and intention.</p><p><strong>The 7.5oz Loopwheel T-Shirt with and without pocket</strong></p><p>Knitted on traditional loopwheel machines in Japan. Heavyweight. No side seams. Built to age alongside the denim.</p><p><strong>The Indigo Bandana</strong></p><p>Indigo-dyed fabric with white tiger print. A<br/>subtle extension of the 684 identity.</p><p>The 684 collection is not about decoration.<br/>It is about cohesion.</p>",
        "heading_size": 100,
